        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A staff of water is most often made of driftwood, sometimes lacquered blue. Carved versions often have a wave pattern. The staff smells of rain or brine. While wielding a staff of water, you have resistance 10 to fire.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spout]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Create Water]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Hydraulic Push]</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Quench]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Water Walk]</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Aqueous Orb]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wall of Water]</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Crashing Wave]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Hydraulic Torrent]</em></li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Control Water]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Geyser]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
